pr_body:
Message Insights Worker
- Novelty & sentiment analysis models integrated
- Provides sentiment & novel message counts for specified _insight_days_ duration
- Calculates mean deviation from past values
- Anomaly detection on sentiment trends to provide anomaly timestamps
- Populates message_analysis, message_analysis_summary tables
- Sends insights to Auggie
- Added default housekeeper & worker blocks to config

Corresponding Jupyter notebooks added
